      "webPublicationDate":"2013-10-30T16:00:01Z",
      "webTitle":"Postmodernism killed the avant garde. Lady Gaga is no substitute for Lou Reed | Suzanne Moore",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/oct/30/postmodernism-avant-garde-lady-gaga-lou-reed-x-factor",
